data.description: This freshly remodeled and painted Park Model with a nice open Floor Plan is looking for a new owner. Come and be impressed by the beautiful flooring, soft colors, nice lighting, and lovely furniture that this home has to offer. Amazing Master bedroom, with queen bed, and lovely decor. Lots of closet space here. Half bath for when company visits! Pull out sleeper in living room. Nice laundry room with full size washer and dryer. Located on B street in a very quiet area of the community. Palmetto Palms is a young active 55 community, offering tennis, pickleball, volleyball, 2 pools, library, clubhouse and so much more! Located close to beaches and Sanibel Island. This community has it all!
